According to the ACL (Association for Computational Linguistics) citation style, the citation for the Wikipedia page on Reddit would look like this:

Here's an example of how you can write a plaintext citation for the Wikipedia page on Reddit in ACL style:

(Wikipedia contributors, "Reddit", accessed March 13, 2023, https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reddit.)

In this plaintext citation, "Wikipedia contributors" is the author, "Reddit" is the title of the web page, "accessed March 13, 2023" indicates the date when you accessed the page, and the URL of the page is included at the end of the citation.

As for the source of ACL format guidelines, you can refer to the following URL:

